# 📚 Course Registration System

A **Java Swing-based Course Registration System** that enables students to register for courses while allowing administrators to manage course details efficiently. The application uses **JDBC** for database connectivity and **MySQL** as the backend database.

---

## 🌟 Project Overview

The Course Registration System is designed to simplify the academic course enrollment process. It provides a user-friendly interface for managing students, courses, and registrations while ensuring data is securely stored in a MySQL database.

This project was developed as part of my academic learning to strengthen my knowledge of **Java**, **JDBC**, **MySQL**, and **GUI application development**.

---

## ✨ Features

- 👨‍🎓 Student Registration
- 📚 Course Enrollment
- ➕ Add New Courses
- ✏️ Update Course Details
- ❌ Delete Courses
- 🔍 View Available Courses
- 🗂️ Student Course Management
- 🗄️ MySQL Database Integration
- ✅ Input Validation
- 🖥️ User-Friendly Java Swing Interface

