## ⚙️ Prerequisites

Before running this project, make sure you have:

- Java JDK 8 or above
- MySQL Server
- MySQL Connector/J
- Java IDE (Eclipse, IntelliJ IDEA, NetBeans, or VS Code)

---

## 🚀 Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/balazzx/Course-Registration-System.git
```

2. Open the project in your preferred Java IDE.

3. Create the required MySQL database.

4. Update the database credentials in `DBConnection.java`.

5. Add the required JDBC and JavaMail JAR files (if not already included).

6. Run `CourseSystemJDBC.java`.

